IMPLEMENTATION Draw

IMPORT Settings COMPLETELY
       Layout COMPLETELY
       Seq[posWord] COMPLETELY
       Seq[point] COMPLETELY
       WinCanvasEditor COMPLETELY
       WinConfig COMPLETELY

DEF draw(posWords) == 
        text( pos(this) ) 
        with (text(text(this)) ++ anchor(west) ++ font(stdFont)) ++ draw(rt(posWords))
    WHERE 
        this == ft(posWords)

DEF draw(<>) == {}